<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>真心話大冒險 - 派對破冰神器</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        body { font-family: '微軟正黑體', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; }
        .gradient-bg { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-900">

    <header class="gradient-bg text-white py-20 px-6 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6">真心話大冒險</h1>
        <p class="text-xl mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">喝酒聚會必備！最刺激的破冰神器，讓大家快速升溫，尷尬瞬間變狂歡！</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
            <button class="bg-white text-purple-700 font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:scale-105 transition-transform text-lg">iOS 下載</button>
            <button class="bg-white text-purple-700 font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:scale-105 transition-transform text-lg">Android 下載</button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="py-16 px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">為什麼派對少不了它？</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🧊</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">極速破冰</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">再尷尬的場合也能瞬間熱絡，讓陌生人變成好朋友。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🍻</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">酒局助興</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">酒精加持下的真心話，讓聚會氣氛來到最高點！</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🔥</div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">多樣挑戰</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600">數千種創意挑戰，保證你的聚會從不冷場。</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 bg-gray-900 text-white text-center px-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">準備好挑戰底線了嗎？</h2>
        <button class="bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-500 py-4 px-12 rounded-lg font-bold text-xl transition-colors">立即安裝 App</button>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-8 text-center text-gray-500 text-sm">
        &copy; 2026 真心話大冒險. Enjoy Responsibly.
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
